AUDIO: '&lt;b&gt;done over the past decades.&lt;/b&gt; NVIDIA is doubling almost every year, not only in terms of power, but also in terms of output. And now the question is what is stopping additional AI'

[00:27] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'which allows to do a cleaner and more efficient world. And there are two things. There\'s energy and power, because the data centers for AI are'

[00:39] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'extremely power-hungry. Skeleton, being a specialist in mission-critical power and having installations of hundreds of megawatts already in the field in the US, in Europe, in Asia,'

[00:52] [scene:talk]
